translation: Not possible. It's a long story, but we can't go back, and we can't stop. We're five days out. You have that long to find us a safe way in. After that, we run out of rations.
speaker: Bellamy

trigedasleng: Las mori! 'So na hon kliron-de op kom sheidgeda - den 'so na jomp in.
translation: Final rations! We'll reach the valley at nightfall - then we attack.
speaker: Miller

trigedasleng: Omon gon oson.
translation: All of me for all of us.
speaker: Miller

trigedasleng: Sofon, beja. En's ku.
speaker: Man

trigedasleng: Belomi, skai drag em, hola! Yu sen ai in?
translation: Bellamy, goddamn it, come in! Do you read me?
speaker: Echo

trigedasleng: Yu laik ridiyo Heda-de?
speaker: Echo

trigedasleng: Ekou, daun's pleni.
speaker: Madi

trigedasleng: ...Nomon?
speaker: Gaia

trigedasleng: Ai kamp hir, ai goufa.
speaker: Indra

trigedasleng: Yu souda klir ai of.
translation: You have to let me go.
speaker: Gaia

trigedasleng: No. Wonkru na komba raun gon yumi. 'Mo na throu daun. Jos ste gonen kom liwa mou, en-
translation: No. Wonkru will come for us. They'll fight. Just hold on a little longer, and-
speaker: Indra

trigedasleng: 'Mo nou na komba hir. Wonkru ste shada... Ai gonplei ste odon.
translation: They won't come. Wonkru is broken... My fight is over.
speaker: Gaia

trigedasleng: Wonkru ste shada.
speaker: Octavia

trigedasleng: Omon gon oson.
translation: All of me, for all of us.
speaker: Octavia & Indra

trigedasleng: Heda don komba raun!
speaker: Brell

trigedasleng: Mens mea fiat mens tua.
speaker: Gaia & Madi

trigedasleng: Ste radon.
speaker: Echo

trigedasleng: GYON AU!!!
speaker: Madi

trigedasleng: Teik emo au.
speaker: Madi

trigedasleng: En em bilaik mouda Madi gaf in kigon em levo ogeda kom ai.
translation: Which is why Madi needs to continue her training with me
speaker: Gaia

trigedasleng: Wof em teik em nila reya? O, em'ilaik, ge jok op kom fayaslais?
translation: What if she skins her knee? Or, I don't know, gets a paper cut?
speaker: Gaia

trigedasleng: Ai hod yu in, Klok.
speaker: Madi

trigedasleng: Flish em of. Ai gaf in chich yu op soulou. Kom nau.
translation: Get rid of her. I need to talk to you alone. Now.
speaker: Bellamy

trigedasleng: Ai sin in feis-de kom keryon ai don rip klin ona flashpa, nou ona fleta.
translation: I see the faces of the people I've killed when I dream, not in the mirror.
speaker: Bellamy

trigedasleng: Badan yu Heda op o wan op!
Bida airein nou na kep yu klin!
Nat ai drein yu jus daun!
Vosenshou.
Nou fiya ai op nodotaim nowe!
translation: Don't ever lay hands on me again!

trigedasleng: Yu nou ste kamp raun hir, you. Wof emo don sin in yu jus?
translation: You're not supposed to be here. What if they had seen your blood?

trigedasleng: Yu gonplei ste odon.
Fleimon-de laik ai shouna... En ai laik Fleimon-de.
translation: The Flame is my guide... And I am the Flame.

trigedasleng: Weron emo noda Heda?
Em bilaik yumi soulou nau.
translation: It's just you and me now.

trigedasleng: Foshou yu Seda don tel yu na fig op shanen voudon. Yu dula'm op?
translation: I'm sure your Seda told you to think good thoughts. Are you?

trigedasleng: Yu Seda get in non nowe. Ain seintaim. Em don trana hod ai daun. Yu laik Heda. Yu don hed fous op. Yu don kep Wonkru klin.
translation: Your teacher knows nothing. Neither did mine. He tried to hold me back. You're the Commander. You led an army. You saved Wonkru.

trigedasleng: Em fir in yu uf. Em gaf in hod yu daun. Ai Seda don's trana hod ai daun, den ai don frag em op. Yu souda frag yun op.
translation: She fears your power. She wants to control you. My teacher was trying to control me, so I killed him. You must kill her.

trigedasleng: Yu fir raun bilaik yu na ste soulou nodotaim. Kom we em don lok yu op.
translation: You're scared that you'll be alone again. Like before she found you.

trigedasleng: Ba yu nou na ste soulou. Teik ai gouba raun yu soncha ona sheid...
translation: But you won't be. Let me be your light in the darkness...

trigedasleng: Sis ai meika op... En ogeda yumi na teik daun disha houd, seim bilaik lason.
translation: Take my hand... And together we will conquer this world, like we did the last.

trigedasleng: Dula'm daun.
Frag em op. Em laik won we noumou na hon yu baman in.
translation: Kill her. It's the only way to get your revenge.

trigedasleng: Daun's kwelen. Heda nou beda-
translation: That was weak. A Commander should never-

trigedasleng: Tel ai hana frag emo op ogeda.
translation: Tell me how to kill them all.

trigedasleng: Ai fos seda.
Sou thosti na bos ai in em don teik ai gon bonij.
translation: So desperate for me to conform that he kept me in chains.

trigedasleng: Fou em frag yu op, kos em sou na dula'm daun.
translation: Before she kills you, because she will.

trigedasleng: Yumi gada in bosh diyo na hash au.
translation: We have a lot to talk about.
speaker: Kane

trigedasleng: Mebi oso na hit choda op nodotaim.
Nou Blodreina nowe.
speaker: Octavia

trigedasleng: Yu gonplei ste odon.
speaker: Indra

trigedasleng: Taim don kom op. Mema yu in: Daunpuden-de laik popop noumou...
translation: It's time. Remember, the execution is only a distraction...
speaker: Gaia

trigedasleng: En frag emo op ogeda.
Nestam, ai frag emo op ogeda.
translation: Next time, I kill them all.

trigedasleng: Osir na gyon au gon girgeda na lok op leja kom Beka! Ste kiken kom taim osir kom op!
translation: We're going to the machine shop to get Becca's book! Stay alive until we get there!

trigedasleng: Nau gouba raun kom yu fleim ai klin!
translation: Now act like you hate me!

trigedasleng: Yu laik Natblida...
Madi, no! Ste kamp raun ai, Madi. Fronzeda op.
translation: Madi, no! Stay with me, Madi. Focus.

trigedasleng: Kom nau gon feva... Ai laik yu.
speaker: Sheidheda

trigedasleng: Bak emo op, en lein yo au.
translation: Move them back, and get into formation.
speaker: Indra

trigedasleng: Emo gonplei ste odon.
speaker: Gaia

trigedasleng: Weron yu fous kamp raun, Indra? Mebi bilaik non gaf in sis yu au na tromp noda kru klin hashta emo hayon?
translation: Where's your army, Indra? Could it be no one wanted to help you lie to another people about their god?
speaker: KNIGHT

trigedasleng: Bilaik tridropa ona yu loga.
translation: There's a spider on your shoulder.
speaker: Indra

trigedasleng: Sos yu nou na rip ai klin.
translation: Too bad you can't kill me.
speaker: Russheda

trigedasleng: Ai wona in, yu shela don gon nila taim ai don teik Trikru daun?
translation: I wonder, did your parents kneel when I conquered Trikru?
speaker: Russheda

trigedasleng: Taim yu souda get em in, ai nontu don slip daun ona brolgeda. Taim enon wan daun, sha, ai nomon don gon nila. Em don gon kwelen ona ai.
translation: If you must know, my father had already died in the battle. When it was over, yes, my mother did kneel. I thought her weak for it.
speaker: Indra

trigedasleng: Sich don gon daun, Seya.
speaker: Lindo

trigedasleng: Du don breik in ona mesa en jak fayagon-de op.
translation: Someone broke into the armory and stole the guns.
speaker: Lindo

trigedasleng: Taim?
speaker: Indra

trigedasleng: Lasnat. Houlas kombou-de. Er shuda oso don gada op.
translation: Last night. The entire locker. Every weapon we'd collected.
speaker: Lindo

trigedasleng: Bloka-de laksen?
speaker: Indra

trigedasleng: Emo nou'n kamp raun ouder. Non'on sin in non nowe.
translation: They weren't there. No one saw a thing.
speaker: Lindo

trigedasleng: Ona ai.
speaker: Indra

trigedasleng: Sonop, you.
speaker: Russheda

trigedasleng: Ai's trein op yufa. Mochof hasht’asen. Sos, nami. Rezen-de don ste krei os, you. Hofli ai na dula’m op nodotaim.
translation: I'm recovering fine. Thank you for asking. Pity, though. Resurrection was wonderful. I would have liked to do it again.
speaker: Russheda

trigedasleng: Indra! Osir don komba raun! Kaina trompen loud yu na slog au ona 'sir deyon?!
translation: Indra! We're all here! What grand lie do you have for us today?!
speaker: Knight

trigedasleng: Den weron Heda kamp raun?
speaker: Knight

trigedasleng: Nou bilaik Heda noumou.
speaker: Indra

trigedasleng: Chof gon yu en yu nomfri. Osir get em in. Den hakom oso kamp raun hir?
translation: Thanks to you and your daughter. We know. Then why are we here?
speaker: Knight

trigedasleng: En's radon nou bilaik Heda, ba nou trip yo op, ai sou hed yo op.
translation: There may be no Commander, but make no mistake, I am in command.
speaker: Indra

trigedasleng: Chomouda osir beda mafta yu op? Yu’n bastab osir daun! Tromp osir op! En nau yu na as raun na hed osir op?!
translation: Why should we follow you? You betrayed us! Lied to us! And now you ask to lead us?!
speaker: Knight

trigedasleng: Ai nou ste as raun.
speaker: Indra

trigedasleng: Oso laik Wonkru. Nou bodaban kru nowe. Oso don gyon op kom folau kom bonka en wing au gon skaifaya na lok op brana hou. Bilaik hazod hir na teik oso daun taim oso speis au gon daun.
translation: We are Wonkru. Not separate clans. We rose from the ashes of the bunker and flew across the stars to find a new home. There are threats here that will defeat us if we fail to remember that.
speaker: Indra

trigedasleng: Nait, en's ona yu na kleim asen fayagon in kom honon-de.
translation: Knight, you're in charge of getting the missing guns back from the prisoners.
speaker: Indra

trigedasleng: Klok, chon em bilaik?
speaker: Niylah

trigedasleng: Bonka weron yo’n shak op sis yiron. Dison laik koken hedswisha seda don stan em op.
translation: The bunker you lived in for six years. This is the crazy cult leader who built it.
speaker: Clarke

trigedasleng: Ha yu na ge'da'n in?
speaker: Niylah
